<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-10">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Billing Overview</h1>

  <p class="mb-4">
    <%= link_to 'replicate.info', root_path, class: "text-blue-600 font-semibold" %> uses monthly, pay-as-you-go billing at <strong>$30 USD per user</strong>, per month.
    Your first full calendar month is free.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-4">
    There are no feature restrictions, upsells, or tiered pricing — just one flat rate per user.
    You can convert that price to other currencies
    <%= link_to 'here', 'https://www.xe.com/currencyconverter/', target: "_blank", class: "text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium hover:underline hover:underline-offset-4 decoration-1 transition" %>.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-4">
    No credit card is required to sign up. Toward the end of your trial, you’ll receive an email asking whether you'd like to continue.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-12">
    Invoices are sent on the first business day of each month, based on the total number of users at that time.
    This includes invited users who haven’t engaged yet.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Annual Pricing</h2>
  <p class="mb-12">
    Prefer a flat annual fee? Just email your estimated usage to
    <%= mail_to 'support@replicate.info', 'support@replicate.info', class: "text-blue-600 font-semibold" %> for an offer.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Payments & Invoicing</h2>
  <p class="mb-4">
    Payments are processes with Stripe — via credit card or ACH. You can opt in to autopay at any time.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-4">
    Invoices include your company name, number of users, and full remittance details for finance teams.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-12">
    Access may be paused if payment isn’t received within 30 days of invoice delivery.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Other Notes</h2>
  <p class="mb-4">
    The platform does not charge VAT. If required, you can self-account under reverse charge rules.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-8">
    For questions or to request a W-9, email
    <%= mail_to 'support@replicate.info', 'support@replicate.info', class: "text-blue-600 font-semibold" %>.
  </p>

  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
    <%= link_to 'Terms of Service', '/terms', class: "underline" %> &nbsp;&nbsp;•&nbsp;&nbsp;
    <%= link_to 'Privacy Policy', '/privacy', class: "underline" %>
  </p>
</div>